---
// src/components/sections/AboutHero.astro
---

<header class="about-hero bg-tech-dark">
    <div class="bg-base"></div>
    <div class="tech-grid-bg"></div>
    <div class="ambient-glow"></div>

    <div class="container relative-z animate-enter">
        <span class="section-badge accent">Nuestra Esencia</span>
        <h1 class="section-title lg">
            Orquestamos tecnología para <br />
            <span class="text-span gradient highlight-brand accent not-mobile"
                >trascender en la enseñanza.</span
            >
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">
            En Isinova, no solo desplegamos código; construimos la
            infraestructura crítica que sostiene el futuro académico de Chile,
            uniendo ingeniería de clase mundial con la realidad educativa local.
        </p>

        <dl class="hero-stats-quick">
            <div class="q-stat" tabindex="0">
                <dt>+12</dt>
                <dd>Años de Experiencia</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="q-stat" tabindex="0">
                <dt>99.9%</dt>
                <dd>Uptime Garantizado</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="q-stat" tabindex="0">
                <dt>+50k</dt>
                <dd>Alumnos Activos</dd>
            </div>
        </dl>
    </div>
</header>

<style>
    .about-hero {
        padding: 12rem 0 8rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
    }

    .hero-desc {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: #94a3b8;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .hero-stats-quick {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 3rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .q-stat {
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        cursor: default;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .q-stat:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .q-stat dt {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        display: block;
    }

    .q-stat dd {
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .relative-z {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
    }

    /* ANIMACIONES */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
    .animate-enter {
        animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) forwards;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .about-hero {
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .about-hero {
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .hero-desc {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .hero-stats-quick {
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .q-stat {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }
    }
</style>
